    "Body": "???????????????????????? Featured Job Opportunity Senior Product Manager - C2C at OKEx Eddie March 12, 2020 OKEx is a world-leading digital asset exchange, providing advanced financial services to traders worldwide leveraging blockchain technology. Our platform offers spot & derivatives trading helping traders optimize their strategy. It provides a safe, reliable and stable environment for digital assets trading via web interface and mobile app by adopting GSLB, and distributed server clusters. We believe blockchain technology will eliminate barriers to transactions, increase the efficiency of transactions across society, and eventually have a significant impact on the global economy. We strive to achieve something that changes the world and never stop to innovate and improve on our customer experience. Job Description Despite the Global Economy downturn, the Blockchain development thrives! As our Hong Kong business taking up a strategic position, we are now looking to build a new Product team from scratch, of course with a lot of help from the Product experts from different offices! The high-level job objective would be to improve our C2C products for a number of currencies. Come onboard and speak to us now! How the daily work looks like: Responsible for functional planning of financial products, output prototypes and product requirements documents and check system functionality, with a focus on the C2C fiat product or payment solutions Responsible for the establishment of overseas c2c fiat currency to crypto transaction business lines, including front-end style design, standardized transaction ecological construction, overseas user growth and design of business operation tools Research on identity authentication systems of different countries, responsible for the output and implementation of anti-money laundry risk control strategies on overseas c2c fiat currency trading Track international user needs, optimize overseas user experiences and interactions, discover differences between Chinese and international user preferences, identify issues, and follow up on product upgrades Liaise with product, technical, business development, social media, community, brand public relations and other teams to coordinate project progress; Monitor and analyze competitor products and enhance our product's competitiveness and user experience; Ideal candidate must have: Extensive experience of using and designing international Internet products Bachelor's degrees or above with 4+ years of experience in Internet product and mobile product design and optimization, with global vision Has strong business judgment and market insight, can clearly and accurately sort out business layout and overall strategy Perfect project management awareness on the whole process from demand identification, project implementation analysis, function design, project follow-up, quality acceptance, online release to performance evaluation; Strong logic analysis and execution abilities, responsible and can work under pressure; Willing to travel from time to time, mainly to Beijing Fluent English, Mandarin is a plus but not mandatory Nice to have: Strong interest in blockchain and cryptocurrencies; Experience in design of ecommerce transaction systems or payment settlement systems preferred; ???????????????????????? Hong Kong ???????????????????????? Visa Sponsor ", 
